maintainer info
===============

- to prepare a release:
  - update the release number in configure.ac to X.Y and commit
  - create a simple tag with 'svn copy trunk tags/release-X.Y'
  - in directory tags/release-X.Y, do:
    ./autogen.sh
    ./configure
    fakeroot make dist
  - upload resulting oftc-services-X.Y.tar.gz to distribution site

- to interact with subversion:
  - remove all generated files
    make maintainer-clean
  - see what's changed:
    svn diff
  - add/remove files as necessary:
    svn add <file>
    svn remove <file>
  - commit changes:
    svn commit
